Package it.polimi.ingsw.psp44.server.controller

Class CardController

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.psp44.server.controller.CardController
  • public class CardController
extends java.lang.Object
    This class menages the turn of a player. Each turn is a deterministic finite state machine, where the states are associated with the actions that the player can perform.
